WEBVTT

NOTE Captions for the founder message video. Timings are approximate.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.500
Hello there. I'm Kevin, the founder of CareMetric CareBase.

2
00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:12.000
For over twenty years, I've led and consulted for senior care organizations.

3
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Five years in nursing home management, and the last seventeen in hospice.

4
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:24.000
I hold a master's degree in social work, and a doctorate in naturopathic medicine.

5
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:33.000
I'm also a certified medication administration trainer of nearly ten years,
a certified hospice and palliative care administrator,

6
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:39.000
a certified diabetic educator, and a nationally certified guardian.

7
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:46.000
All that time, working alongside personal care homes, I kept seeing the same thing.

8
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:52.500
They carry the same responsibilities as nursing homes.
But they never had the same tools. Until now.

9
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:59.500
My whole career, I built my reputation on two things.
Strict compliance. And real patient care.

10
00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:05.500
But I can't be in every facility at once. So I built the software that lets me be.

11
00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:13.000
CareBase handles what keeps you up at night. Compliance paperwork.
Resident care. Billing and financial management.

12
00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:19.000
Staff education. And your state documentation. All in one place.

13
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:26.000
So when the state surveyor walks through your door,
you don't panic. You're already ready.

14
00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:34.000
This is the result of twenty years of executive management and consulting.
It's the software you always hoped for, and could never find. Welcome to CareBase.
